data.caption: Announcement under Regulation 30 (LODR)-Investor Presentation
data.news_body:
Dear Sir,
Sub: Presentation to Investor/ Analyst on the Audited Standalone and Consolidated
Financial Results of the Bank for the quarter and year ended 31st March 2021
As required under Regulation 30 of SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements)
regulations, 2015, we are attaching herewith, an Investor / Analyst Presentation on the Audited
Standalone and Consolidated Financial Results of the Bank for the quarter and financial year
ended 31st March 2021, business updates for the period ended 31st March 2021 and press
release. The same has been published on the Bank's website also.
Kindly take the same on your record.
